  "management45": "Critical operational constraints are flagged at 12 airports right now. Engine anti-ice operations are flagged at Craiova (CRA/LRCV). Across base airports: 2 critical, 5 high, 11 medium, 21 normal. Key bases needing attention include Chişinău (RMO/LUKK), Bucharest Henri Coandă (OTP/LROP) and Craiova (CRA/LRCV); plus 4 other bases. 11 additional base airports are at medium severity and should be monitored closely. At base airports, the dominant pattern is fog / freezing fog, very low visibility and RVR limitations  — most notably around Craiova (CRA/LRCV), Bucharest Băneasa Aurel Vlaicu (BBU/LRBS) and Bucharest Henri Coandă (OTP/LROP). Network hotspots: Craiova (CRA/LRCV), Lennart Meri Tallinn (TLL/EETN), Turku (TKU/EFTU), Oslo-Gardermoen (OSL/ENGM), Sandefjord Airport, Torp (TRF/ENTO) and 7 others. Primary drivers: low cloud base, mist and fog / freezing fog. Expected impact is reduced runway capacity with higher delay and diversion risk, especially where visibility/RVR and cloud base are very low.",
